# Quality

- Every new feature needs tests in the same PR/change
- After code changes, run `./scripts/check.sh` (tsc + eslint for client and server)
- Run `./scripts/test.sh` when adding or changing behaviour
- Use Prettier via ESLint (`eslint-plugin-prettier`); format with `./scripts/format.sh` if needed
